    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shoes that are an element of Greek folk dress. The tip of the shoe is formed as an upstanding point, on top of which a pompom is attached.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
